Cyberpunk style: A dark neon-lit server room with towering data stacks, streams of glowing cyan and magenta data flowing like waterfalls between massive black monolithic servers. In the foreground, a lone terminal screen casts an eerie glow, surrounded by floating holographic XML brackets and cascading file icons dissolving into digital particles. Rain streaks across a grimy window in the background, reflecting the pulsing lights. The atmosphere is moody and technical, with visible network cables snaking like vines through the machinery, and small indicator lights blinking in rhythmic patterns across endless rack-mounted equipment.
